<seg id="224">As part of the preparation of parallel audits, a coordination meeting of representatives of the SAO, the Czech Republic and representatives of the SAO SR took place in the first half of July 2005.</seg>
<seg id="225">The participants of this meeting got acquainted with the legislation in the field of VAT in both countries and the integration of the electronic system VIES into national databases.</seg>
