<seg id="227">Both parties agreed that the cooperation will focus on the following areas: a) verification of the validity and accuracy of the VAT number of persons registered for VAT in the Czech Republic, resp. SR in intra-community deliveries; b) verification of data on intra-community acquisitions specified in the DAP of the payer in the Czech Republic using information from summary reports (hereinafter referred to as “SH”) of payers from the Slovak Republic contained in the VIES system, and vice versa; c) exchange of information between tax administrations in the Czech Republic and in the Slovak Republic on completed business transactions.</seg>
