<seg id="172">In the integration center, clients pay for all accommodation costs and eat individually.</seg>
<seg id="173">Persons with recognized refugee status have the same rights and obligations as Czech citizens and have the same access to social security.</seg>
<seg id="174">5.1.1 Costs of asylum facilities</seg>
<seg id="175">For the comparison of asylum facilities, it was chosen as the best telling indicator of the amount of costs per physical day of stay.</seg>
