<seg id="1">Amendment No. 1 to the Apartment Sublease Agreement dated 13 May 2016</seg>
<seg id="2">695604/3017, Radimova 8, Prague 6, Postal Code: 169 00, as a tenant on the one hand (hereinafter referred to as the "tenant") and Karolína Černá, row no. 136205/891 apartment: Alfrédova 13, Prague 4, postal code: 142 00 as a subtenant on the other hand (hereinafter referred to as the "subtenant") together also as "contracting parties" this Addendum No. 1 to the Contract for sublease of an apartment of 13 May 2016 (hereinafter referred to as "Supplement No. 1")</seg>
